{"tid":660699,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"質疑警教招供　辯方：被告錄口供似低能仔","createTime":"2018-05-11T02:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T03:43:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c9322f51140566ce1bab42e87c8cc212e59bf594","tid":660699,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T02:20:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180511/20387357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180511%2F20387357&d=E3UvubJckY66CQjiX2yg4JUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=6230b450\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180511%2F20387357&h=dd6ab499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180511/20387357</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月11日 <br />\n<br />\n質疑警教招供　辯方：被告錄口供似低能仔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180511/large/11la8p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180511%2Flarge%2F11la8p3.jpg&h=75fd8f1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【旺角騷亂案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】2016年大年初二旺角騷亂案續審，第五被告林倫慶（圖）的大狀結案陳詞，指林在錄影會面招供時答非所問，全因答案是警方事先準備，「𠵱個係警員想聽嘅答案」，又指林在會面時反應甚慢，「好似背書咁，好似機械人，沒不敬之意，有啲似低能仔」，提醒陪審團要「寧縱莫枉」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指完全答非所問<br />\n<br />\n林被警方以暴動罪拘捕時，警誡下稱「阿sir，我嗰晚有落旺角，我見人哋執起地下嘅磚掟，咁我咪跟住掟囉。至於新屯門中心呢度，我好少返嚟，我租咗附近南豐工業城第4座一個單位，喺嗰度住多」。<br />\n<br />\n大狀王國豪指林突自揭並非居於新屯門中心是答非所問，是警方預先準備好的答案，至於林在警察「流水簿」上簽名招供，大狀指「離晒譜，個簽名好似鬼畫符咁」，實是林不自願及受壓之下筆迹。<br />\n<br />\n大狀強調林於案發後一個月才被捕，僅一名電影報刊辦督察聲稱從fb截圖中認出林並向警方舉報，惟督察只在案發前半年一個動漫展見過林幾十秒，後來再透過警方拍攝片段認人，反問陪審團：「隔住個螢光幕認人係咪準確？」<br />\n<br />\n至於審訊期間突錄口供稱認出林的警員，大狀質疑他從沒向上司或同袍透露事件，要求陪審團考慮其證供是否可接受。<br />\n<br />\n五名被告均已完成結案陳詞，案件下周一續審，屆時法官開始引導陪審團。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCCC408/16<br />\n■記者蘇曉欣  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n慶委會再霸維園阻7.1遊行起步　民陣申公民廣場做終點半年無回音<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n東北收地賠償　港府加碼2.4億元"},{"pid":"e58f629d27e75460a1c8bf51ce11eaa2ade16338","tid":660699,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T02:26:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89b47f68310d5750bd554fca17301fcf15bd416d","tid":660699,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T02:29:45.000Z","msg":"M記經理?"},{"pid":"0b56063c47ebbed6a6ed85ddb1869975de7a0820","tid":660699,"uid":887,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e58f629d27e75460a1c8bf51ce11eaa2ade16338","tid":660699,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T02:26:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T02:32:33.000Z","msg":"係呀係呀<br />\n最叻都係兩登啲鍵國戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74975881feb15660335b07c2f84da22aebcc5cb","tid":660699,"uid":156511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T02:32:56.000Z","msg":"有樣睇"},{"pid":"5bc13369acee126d687332276cf3782db3b04008","tid":660699,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T03:23:59.000Z","msg":"剪下頭髮啦"},{"pid":"500196007601cc8323bea7d83e0c4320f6f3b644","tid":660699,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T03:25:49.000Z","msg":"狗賊老屈成性"},{"pid":"0ddbfe8403b321df5567dc16adff50e22f860f85","tid":660699,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T03:33:06.000Z","msg":"為左辯護，要話被告係低能仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1ccce3a274798bb9ff441495cb52918008f847","tid":660699,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ddbfe8403b321df5567dc16adff50e22f860f85","tid":660699,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T03:33:06.000Z","msg":"為左辯護，要話被告係低能仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T03:43:28.